title: Episode 288: The Art of Overcoming your Boysh*t Ways (Feat. Kountry Wayne)
itunes:title: Episode 288: The Art of Overcoming your Boysh*t Ways (Feat. Kountry Wayne)
description:
Comedian Kountry Wayne is here to promote his absolutely hilarious Instagram skits, his book, and his films. Wayne gets open and honest throughout the entire episode, sharing his secrets to having all his baby mothers get along, how he just learned about his 10th child, his secrets in bed, and much more. Kountry even shoots his shot at Meg the Stallion for Valentines Day! Enjoy!
